## рҹ“Ӣ Overview

This project was born from a real operational need: there was no structured process for managing failures across teams. What started as manual Excel spreadsheets evolved into a fully automated system integrating **Slack, Google Sheets, n8n, and Looker Studio**.

The system runs 24/7 with zero manual intervention, serving 4 business areas (Mature Sales, Publications, Buyer, and Insurance) and 15 Team Leaders.

